~~انظر: m.m. watt: muhammad at mecca, oxford, 1960, p.xv; and his «the
~~materials used by ibn ishaq» in b. lewis and p.m. holtfield (ed):
~~historians of the middle east, london, 1962, pp.23-24 (4) انظر:
